@node FDT_ADV "FinalDT - Advanced Users"

   !!! THIS SECTION IS FOR ADVANCED USERS ONLY !!!

   FinalDT can be used also inside YOUR ARexx script. 
   Infact, program template is the following:

    FinalDT PORT/A,PAGE/A,FILENAME

    PORT     - Port name (because, every FinalWriter window has its own port)
    PAGE     - Page number where to place graphic.
    FILENAME - Name of the picture to load. If it is not provided, FinalDT
               will open a file requester.

    
    So you can use FinalDT inside your ARexx script by simply providing 
    those params. Study carefully FinalDT.rexx to see how to know which
    port and page number has to be passed to FinalDT.
@endnode
